I WOKE UP IN BITCH MOOOOOOODE! 
And #stronger than ever! 
.
Over here in this community, WE are not weak. 
WE work hard. 
WE train! 
WE #FIGHT for what we believe in!
#WE do what’s necessary (in any situation)
WE are #strong 
WE are #brave 
WE believe in ourselves#
WE know our worth and don’t ever ANYONE make you feel less than
WE are #strong minded individuals 
And WE do this for OURSELVES  and for our loved ones
and most importantly….
WE don’t give a damn! 
.
Who’s ready to join this army? 
💪
DO you think you have what it takes? 
👊

It may be a harsh reality, but WE  don’t sugarcoat things over here.
WE are dedicated to overcoming and achievement

weak or the weak minded, but the good news is you can change all that and I can help you! You may be cut out for greatness or you may not. There’s only one way to find out 
TRY

🌟 Reflecting on the Past to Motivate the Future 🌟
#tuesdaymotivation💪 
🙏🏻
“Success is built upon the foundation of our past accomplishments. Today, I’m drawing inspiration from this incredible moment with one of the most positive humans I’ve ever had the honor to work & share a stage with…. @thegoodbadguytamatonga from #wrestlekingdom9 in Tokyo Dome when I was part of #BulletClub @njpw1972 
🤩
We have both embarked on a path filled with challenges, sacrifices, and unwavering determination. From THE NJPW stage of wrestling we showcased our skills, passion, and dedication, captivating fans worldwide.
🌎
Let this moment remind us all that greatness is within reach when we embrace our past, learn from it, and use it as fuel for our future aspirations. 
💪
As I continue to channel this same spirit, I urge you to do the same and conquer our own arenas, whether it's in our careers, relationships, or personal growth. Let's tap into the strength and lessons of our past, propelling us towards the extraordinary future we envision.
🚀
Remember, the past is not a limitation but a stepping stone. Embrace it, learn from it, and let it inspire you to reach new heights. Believe in yourself and unleash your potential!

#MotivationTuesday #PastToFuture #Inspiration #BulletClubNJPW"
🔥
I hope this post inspires you and others to use the power of the past to fuel future success!
🙌
Sometimes I have to remind myself what I have accomplished and be grateful for the people that got me there to remind myself to keep going! 
🙏🏻

Life is all about lessons! 
sometimes you think you’re in a safe space and you’re not. That’s a lesson! 
Be more guarded! 
Sometimes you feel the same people that knew you knew you 20 years ago understand you love you and respect you. They know the real you and they love you for that. This is not always true. 
That’s a lesson! Again get that guard up! 
Sometimes you get judged just for being in a beautiful happy grateful mood because you’re so DAMN happy to see people that you haven’t seen in five years. 
Lesson is…. Try to control your excitement so people don’t make assumptions. 
Today I learned a very valuable lesson! God has given me one blessing that one blessing is one true loyal friend. And I’m just very very grateful that I was blessed with at least ONE true loyal friend.
forever grateful for you  @magical.krissy 
🙏🏻
#lifelessons #truefriends #stayguarded #liveandlearn #BEGRATFULFORTHEREALONES
